N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 47.2 - Articles of incorporation to be filed

State Regulations

The petitioner shall file with its application a copy of
its original articles of incorporation and each amendment thereto affecting its
capital structure. Notes
